Jangan panggil aku "adik kecil".

50
00:04:24.547 --> 00:04:25.947
Namaku Justin.

51
00:04:25.947 --> 00:04:28.347
Justin Takamori.

52
00:04:28.347 --> 00:04:30.647
Justin?

53
00:04:30.647 --> 00:04:32.347
Sungguh manis.

54
00:04:32.347 --> 00:04:34.447
Ya, banyak orang mengatakan itu padaku.

55
00:04:35.647 --> 00:04:39.147
Tapi kau lebih manis daripada aku.

56
00:04:39.147 --> 00:04:41.247
Hah?

57
00:04:41.247 --> 00:04:43.547
Senyuman itu, kedipan itu...

